Interface Type

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ArrayType, BitType, DoubleType, EnumType, FloatType, FunctionType, IntType, MemberFunctionType, PointerType, RefType, TemplateType, VoidType
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicArrayType, BasicBitType, BasicCompoundType, BasicDoubleType, BasicEnumType, BasicFloatType, BasicFunctionType, BasicIntType, BasicMemberFunctionType, BasicPointerType, BasicRefType, BasicType, BasicVoidType, LazyType

    public interface Type
    Models a C or C++ type. Symbols have an associated Type.
